
## Create AWS EKS clsuster

## Pre-requisite links
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/eks/latest/userguide/getting-started-eksctl.html

## Create EKS cluster
eksctl create cluster --name ekssecrete_204 --node-type t2.large --nodes 1 --nodes-min 1 --nodes-max 2 --region eu-west-2

## Get EKS Cluster service
eksctl get cluster --name ekssecrete_204 --region eu-west-2

## Get EKS Pod data.
kubectl get pods --all-namespaces

## Delete EKS cluster
eksctl delete cluster --name ekssecrete_204 --region eu-west-2

